Hebrews 2-14 <pb/>Since therefore the children share in flesh and blood, he himself likewise <f>ⓘ</f>partook of the same things, that <f>ⓙ</f>through death he might <f>ⓚ</f>destroy <f>ⓛ</f>the one who has the power of death, that is, the devil,
